{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-218-perfect-right-angled-triangles","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Izazov 218: Trokut za stranice koje imaju savršen pravi ugao","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Razmotriti pravougaoni trougao sa stranicama $a=7$, $b=24$ i $c=25$.</p>\n<p>Površina ovog trougla je 84, što se može podeliti sa brojevima 6 i 28.</p>\n<p>Osim toga je prirodni trokut jer $gcd(a,b) = 1$ i $gcd(b,c) = 1$.</p>\n<p>Pia $c$ je savršen kvadrat.</p>\n<p>Naziva se savršeni trougao stranica ako:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>To je pravougli trougao</li>\n<li>Njegova hipotenuza je savršen kvadrat</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Zove se treća stranica super-savršena ako:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pravougli trougao</li>\n<li>Njegova površina je puta celog broja 6 i 28.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Koliko trouglova sa savršenim stranicama koji imaju $c ≤ {10}^{16}$ postoje, a koji nisu super-savršeni?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4461000cf542c50ff59","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301860,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-218-perfect-right-angled-triangles"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function perfectRightAngledTriangles() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nperfectRightAngledTriangles();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>perfectRightAngledTriangles()</code> treba da vrati <code>0</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(perfectRightAngledTriangles(), 0);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/le